Step 2 is a risk assessment for estimating a single target carbon mitigation rate, ΔQ(t), that can reduce each value of SRCMF{ΔTj, Y} to below its respective Rj tolerance. A formula that summarizes Steps 1 and 2 is as follows:6ΔQi(t)=Function{SRCMF{ΔTj,Yi},Rj:j=1,N}\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
